Himachal Pradesh is home to some of the most beautiful high-altitude lakes, each with its own charm. **Chandratal**, the ‘Moon Lake,’ stuns with its turquoise waters, while **Prashar Lake** mesmerizes with its floating island. **Rewalsar Lake** holds deep spiritual significance, and **Suraj Tal**, near Baralacha Pass, offers stunning Himalayan views. **Kareri Lake** is a trekker’s paradise, surrounded by lush meadows. Whether for adventure or tranquility, these lakes are must-visits. Explore them with **Pahari Yatri** for an unforgettable journey!
